#: buildVars.py:21
msgid "LINE Desktop Accessibility"
msgstr "LINE 電腦版無障礙增強"

#: buildVars.py:24
msgid ""
"Enhances NVDA accessibility support for LINE Desktop on Windows.\n"
"Provides improved navigation for chat lists, messages, contacts, and message input.\n"
"Supports calls, incoming call handling, OCR-assisted reading, message export reading, and AI image description with follow-up questions."
msgstr ""
"增強 NVDA 對 Windows 上 LINE 電腦版的無障礙支援。\n"
"提供對聊天列表、訊息、聯絡人與訊息輸入的改進導覽體驗。\n"
"支援通話、來電處理、OCR 輔助閱讀、訊息匯出閱讀，以及可追問的 AI 圖片描述。"

#: buildVars.py:31
msgid ""
"Added an AI image description dialog with a read-only transcript and follow-up questions.\n"
"Added settings for the image description service, API key, model, and prompt.\n"
"Completed translations and documentation for all supported languages."
msgstr ""
"新增 AI 圖片描述對話視窗，支援唯讀對話紀錄與後續提問。\n"
"新增圖片描述服務、API Key、模型與提示詞設定。\n"
"補齊所有支援語言的翻譯與說明文件。"

